  <histories>
    <history>
      <header>Team intentions</header>
      <text>
        In the PileUp team, we believe that games are a good way to create bonds between people. When we created this project, we thought there is a need in the industry for more cooperative games. Especially for casual games and children oriented games. This was our core intention:  the promise of an adventure that you could share with up to four people, a casual game that could gather the whole family, children and parents alike, in a funny, playful and non-violent space.
      </text>
